eu.wauz.wauzcore.items

Class WauzEquipment

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.wauz.wauzcore.items.WauzEquipment

  • public class WauzEquipment
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that represents a base type of equipment. Also contains static methods to verify or generate equipment items.
    Author:
    Wauzmons
